• Documentation: Proficient in drafting and reviewing HR-related documents, policies, reports, and contracts with precision and legal compliance.
• Personal attributes: Highly detail-oriented, meticulous in daily tasks, and consistently demonstrates a high level of accountability and responsibility in all assignments.

